    "Participants experiencing burnout symptoms may have been either more or less likely to participate, contributing to response bias.",
    "Study duration ranged between 4 weeks and a year.",
    "Studies from across the globe were included with seven studies from the USA, [35] [36] [37] [38] [39] 41, 46 two from the UK, 40, 42 and one each from Canada and South Korea, respectively.",
